HEADWORD: Trimellic
<hw>Tri*mel"lic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>tri-</ets> + L. <ets>mel</ets>, gen. <ets>mellis</ets>,
honey.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Of, pertaining to, or designating,
